{"tid":1879230,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地 咪撚再飲道地","createTime":"2020-02-14T05:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T16:03:17.000Z","uid":106523,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9079f0e82fef63bb9a9cf58f46f67a234025fc59","tid":1879230,"uid":106523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T05:26:28.000Z","msg":"(代fd po)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">匯泉高層藍到黑</span></span><br />\n新年之後死都唔俾home office<br />\n要人返工但喺話買唔到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">紙巾要限住用 收起曬啲酒精消毒液</span><br />\n每人派一個薄到似救救既口罩 仲要唔喺每日派<br />\n而家開始<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">逼人攞假</span> 無晒假就no pay<br />\n出policy話每日都要探熱先入office<br />\n但做咗第一日之後就無人理<br />\n結果兩個同事發燒仲返到工 送埋入醫院先識死<br />\n咁多嘢都安排唔到俾同事 剩喺安排到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">三百萬人仔捐去上海</span></span>抗武漢肺炎<br />\n<br />\n利申：前員工 純粹睇唔過眼出聲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgFr9nR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgFr9nR.jpg&h=b8d63c71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K026pWc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK026pWc.jpg&h=da95b250&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1bf1189a597eb3e02f27d5f8220f9453bb1e7af4","tid":1879230,"uid":106315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"一見到mirinda已經知係紅底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aadbcbdfa8fecdf289fd3bc0353d306a9dbb890","tid":1879230,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"之前唔係話唔係Tvb落廣告定贊助咩"},{"pid":"8e052b644f8fe389ac52136e4e42a2a739f6d86d","tid":1879230,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"一早冇飲 根本屎水嚟"},{"pid":"e7cd01572cefa6b12db99c5d45fb731425252f86","tid":1879230,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T05:3